# Flexible Value-Set Architecture

- For extensible domains, avoid table-per-variant designs.
- Use template/value-set architecture with explicit applicability relations (N:M), not hardcoded `use_*` flags.
- Keep updates synchronized across model, schema, routers, seed loaders/datasets, and impacted UI contracts.
